title: Openstreetmap Geofabrik, Latvia Points of Interest, Latvia, 2008
name: Openstreetmap Geofabrik, Latvia Points of Interest, Latvia, 2008
description: This dataset shows points of interest in Latvia. Features included in this dataset include, libraries, post offices, places of worship, parking, restaurants, cafes, fuel, parking, police, theaters, cinemas, prisons, universities, camp sites and other public places. there are more than 300 points of interest included.
